{
  "text": "The age of typing prompts into a chat window is ending For the past two years the world has marveled at large language models We've asked them questions We've watched them write poems and debug code We've been impressed entertained and sometimes alarmed But here's what most people missed those interactions were never the destination They were the warmup The real shift is happening now And it's not about better prompts or smarter models It's about something far more consequential the transition from AI as a tool you talk to into AI as a system that works Welcome to the era of Agentic AI",
